@startuml
title Radiotherapy Workflow – Simulation Saga

hide empty description

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam Shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F4F6F8
  BorderColor #5A6473
  FontSize 11
  ArrowFontSize 9
  ArrowColor #444444
}

[*] --> Draft

state "1. Intake & Simulation" as SIM {
  state Draft
  state Submitted
  state SimScheduled
  state SimInProgress
  state SimCompleted
}

state Cancelled #FFC0CB : ◎ terminal

' ─── Transitions ─────────────────────────
Draft --> Submitted : SIM-001 SubmitSimulationRequest [User]\n«Doctor»
Submitted --> SimScheduled : SIM-002 ScheduleSimulation [User]\n«SimTech/Scheduler»
SimScheduled --> SimInProgress : SIM-003 StartSimulation [User]\n«SimTech»
SimInProgress --> SimCompleted : SIM-004 SubmitSimulationRecord [User]\n«SimTech»
Submitted --> Cancelled : SIM-005 CancelCase [User]\n«Doctor/Admin»
SimScheduled --> Cancelled : SIM-005 CancelCase [User]\n«Doctor/Admin»
SimInProgress --> Cancelled : SIM-005 CancelCase [User]\n«Doctor/Admin»


@enduml